{"tid":2162794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"擺街站遭大波Man挑釁 快必認踢對方罰款3000元","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T09:57:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"946af2fbcfa9da325e47eaa9d74b416219ddaf47","tid":2162794,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/TSFNSI7ZMNHMFHIUGSCI34I25A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FTSFNSI7ZMNHMFHIUGSCI34I25A%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=e01f223d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FTSFNSI7ZMNHMFHIUGSCI34I25A%2F&h=605ee3ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/TSFNSI7ZMNHMFHIUGSCI34I25A/</a><br />\n<br />\n人民力量副主席「快必」譚得志今年5月在中環碼頭擺街站時，腳踢前來挑釁的「大波Man」石房有。譚今在東區法院承認普通襲擊罪，罰款3,000元。控方庭上透露，有意將譚另涉的5月反國安法遊行案件，與譚另一宗煽惑1月中環集會的粉嶺案件合併處理，惟裁判官指兩案性質不同。譚散庭後提到，粉嶺裁判官早前要求他交出10萬元保釋金，怒指律政司陰謀昭然若揭，意圖將他轉往粉嶺給「釘官」審理。"}]}